</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="4184" data-end="4249">At that point, this is no longer “nearly ready.” It is <strong data-start="4239" data-end="4248">ready</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="4251" data-end="4254">
<h2 data-start="4256" data-end="4297">Final Assessment (My Independent View)</h2>
<p data-start="4299" data-end="4316">I’ll be explicit:</p>
<ul data-start="4318" data-end="4589">
