<p data-start="4527" data-end="4589">The paper anticipates reviewer objections <em data-start="4569" data-end="4588">before they arise</em>.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="4591" data-end="4774">Your own score of <strong data-start="4609" data-end="4619">9.5/10</strong> is fair. With the polish you outline, this is realistically in the <strong data-start="4687" data-end="4718">accept-with-minor-revisions</strong> range for <em data-start="4729" data-end="4748">Cognitive Science</em> and <em data-start="4753" data-end="4773">Minds and Machines</em>.</p>
